Bravo!

5
00:01:20,420 --> 00:01:21,540
Today is your wedding day.

6
00:01:22,100 --> 00:01:23,860
I am ordered to invite you back to the mansion.

7
00:01:32,570 --> 00:01:33,410
Wedding day?

8
00:01:33,960 --> 00:01:35,650
It's time

9
00:01:36,720 --> 00:01:38,120
