41
00:04:27,140 --> 00:04:27,980
No need to say more.

42
00:04:29,020 --> 00:04:29,860
Look at how we are dressed.

43
00:04:29,900 --> 00:04:30,940
Everyone can see it.

44
00:04:31,940 --> 00:04:33,540
Then how can you come to this kind of place,

45
00:04:35,020 --> 00:04:36,300
