46
00:04:37,540 --> 00:04:39,300
Our marriage is just a transaction,

47
00:04:40,260 --> 00:04:41,100
a performance.

48
00:04:42,340 --> 00:04:43,860
Now you have made it like this here.

49
00:04:45,260 --> 00:04:46,620
Do you think you are acting very well?

50
00:04:48,980 --> 00:04:49,820
I...

51
00:04:57,700 --> 00:04:59,260
Young Master, this way please.

52
00:05:00,290 --> 00:05:01,840
Hurry up, girls.

53
00:05:01,840 --> 00:05:03,120
Come on, let's greet guests.

54
00:05:04,390 --> 00:05:06,100
Long time no see.

55
00:05:12,660 --> 00:05:13,500
Miss Xie.

56
00:05:17,540 --> 00:05:18,460
City Lord had orders.

57
00:05:18,660 --> 00:05:19,600
The wind is strong tonight.

58
00:05:19,760 --> 00:05:20,900
He asked you to take a carriage back.

59
00:05:23,060 --> 00:05:24,660
He asked me to parade around

60
00:05:24,700 --> 00:05:26,100
with these rabbits.

61
00:05:27,860 --> 00:05:28,900
What does he mean?

62
00:05:30,260 --> 00:05:32,180
Do you really not know, Mr. Cai?

63
00:05:32,380 --> 00:05:33,260
All right.

64
00:05:33,340 --> 00:05:35,060
Come on, put on your clothes first.

65
00:05:35,700 --> 00:05:36,540
Don't catch a cold.

66
00:05:39,060 --> 00:05:39,900
It's getting cold.

67
00:05:41,700 --> 00:05:42,540
Miss Xie,

68
00:05:42,980 --> 00:05:45,340
today is City Lord's wedding day.

69
00:05:45,940 --> 00:05:48,660
He asked you to take this back.

70
00:05:48,900 --> 00:05:50,500
He actually covered for you.

71
00:05:51,980 --> 00:05:53,300
If Madam finds out

72
00:05:53,380 --> 00:05:55,300
that you stayed by City Lord's side tonight,

73
00:05:55,660 --> 00:05:56,500
you will offend her.

74
00:05:56,660 --> 00:05:59,220
Then you will have a hard time in the future.

75
00:05:59,340 --> 00:06:00,580
Mr. Cai, you're too serious.

76
00:06:01,260 --> 00:06:02,780
Tomorrow is the day we agreed

77
00:06:02,780 --> 00:06:03,820
that I will leave the mansion.

78
00:06:04,740 --> 00:06:05,620
Why bother?

79
00:06:10,540 --> 00:06:11,380
Miss Xie...

80
00:06:16,020 --> 00:06:17,220
- Take care of her.
- Yes, sir.

81
00:06:24,700 --> 00:06:25,540
Ji,

82
00:06:25,820 --> 00:06:26,820
I'll listen to you.

83
00:06:27,180 --> 00:06:28,700
Today is our wedding day.

84
00:06:28,940 --> 00:06:30,380
We haven't completed the ceremony yet.

85
00:06:31,100 --> 00:06:32,060
Go back with me,

86
00:06:32,420 --> 00:06:33,260
OK?

87
00:06:38,580 --> 00:06:41,220
(Yin Ji, four years ago)
Nothing can separate us.

88
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:50,540
Let's go back to the mansion.

89
00:06:51,620 --> 00:06:52,460
OK.

90
00:06:58,820 --> 00:07:02,020
(Xie family colluded with the traitor Yin Qi)

91
00:07:02,220 --> 00:07:03,500
(to plot wrongdoing.)

92
00:07:03,700 --> 00:07:04,740
(Fortunately, they failed.)

93
00:07:05,300 --> 00:07:07,580
(Master Xie has confessed and committed suicide.)

94
00:07:07,780 --> 00:07:09,620
(Three years ago)
(The other 24 persons)

95
00:07:09,940 --> 00:07:11,500
(will be exiled to the border)

96
00:07:11,500 --> 00:07:13,620
- Mother...
- (and stay there forever.)

97
00:07:36,820 --> 00:07:38,460
Where is my mother and my brother?

98
00:07:39,820 --> 00:07:43,980
(Yin Ji, new City Lord of Baiyu City )

99
00:07:48,460 --> 00:07:49,980
(Xie family conspired to rebel.)

100
00:07:50,940 --> 00:07:52,940
(Exile is not enough to atone to the world.)

101
00:07:57,340 --> 00:07:58,180
(Staring from today,)

102
00:07:59,180 --> 00:08:01,300
(be a maid by my side for three years.)

103
00:08:02,140 --> 00:08:03,140
(When three-year term ends,)

104
00:08:04,060 --> 00:08:05,620
(I will send you all to reunite as a family.)

105
00:08:06,740 --> 00:08:08,740
(If you dare to make me unhappy,)

106
00:08:09,740 --> 00:08:11,860
(I will bury your whole family with you.)

107
00:08:14,540 --> 00:08:17,140
Hope that you can keep the promise.

108
00:08:26,490 --> 00:08:32,540
♪A young smile and a promise with you♪

109
00:08:33,520 --> 00:08:39,930
♪A wish hard to fulfill, two silent persons♪

110
00:08:40,430 --> 00:08:45,300
♪Leave one person alone reminiscing old times♪

111
00:08:45,300 --> 00:08:46,860
(Next day)

112
00:08:46,900 --> 00:08:47,740
Xie Yun.

113
00:08:48,020 --> 00:08:48,980
It must be her.

114
00:08:52,220 --> 00:08:54,220
Yes. When I was waiting for you last night,

115
00:08:54,380 --> 00:08:55,860
