116
00:08:55,940 --> 00:08:57,180
Cai Tianxi was by her side.

117
00:08:57,340 --> 00:08:58,180
I'm sure.

118
00:08:58,300 --> 00:08:59,820
She's just the daughter of a traitor,

119
00:09:00,100 --> 00:09:01,980
