120
00:09:02,980 --> 00:09:03,980
If I were her,

121
00:09:04,300 --> 00:09:05,620
I would rather die than surrender.

122
00:09:06,060 --> 00:09:08,060
How dare she still have the nerve to seduce Ji?

123
00:09:09,340 --> 00:09:10,180
My Lady,

124
00:09:10,180 --> 00:09:12,420
