125
00:09:12,540 --> 00:09:14,020
She is just a lowly maid.

126
00:09:14,100 --> 00:09:15,300
She's definitely at your disposal.

127
00:09:15,900 --> 00:09:16,980
That's true.

128
00:09:17,700 --> 00:09:19,820
She used to be the first lady
of Baiyu City. So what?

129
00:09:19,980 --> 00:09:22,460
In the end, I am the winner.

130
00:09:23,140 --> 00:09:24,980
In the past, replying on her status,

131
00:09:25,380 --> 00:09:26,740
she seduced Ji,

132
00:09:27,020 --> 00:09:28,420
and occupied him.

133
00:09:29,500 --> 00:09:31,700
If it weren't for her betrayal,

134
00:09:31,940 --> 00:09:32,860
Ji will never

135
00:09:32,940 --> 00:09:35,140
become dissolute like this.

136
00:09:35,820 --> 00:09:39,460
I must teach this woman a lesson.

137
00:09:43,620 --> 00:09:44,740
Miss! Miss!

138
00:09:45,780 --> 00:09:47,380
Are you having a nightmare again?

139
00:09:50,500 --> 00:09:51,340
Xiuxiu.

140
00:09:51,980 --> 00:09:52,820
Congratulations.

141
00:09:52,820 --> 00:09:53,780
You finally made it through.

142
00:09:54,340 --> 00:09:55,180
Miss,

143
00:09:55,500 --> 00:09:56,340
after returning home,

144
00:09:56,700 --> 00:09:58,220
remember to write me a letter.

145
00:10:08,700 --> 00:10:10,260
1,095 days.

146
00:10:10,900 --> 00:10:11,740
Finally...

147
00:10:13,180 --> 00:10:14,380
I am finally free.

148
00:10:22,340 --> 00:10:23,180
Xiuxiu,

149
00:10:33,780 --> 00:10:34,700
take this bracelet,

150
00:10:35,100 --> 00:10:36,740
sell it and exchange for some money.

151
00:10:38,060 --> 00:10:39,060
After I leave,

152
00:10:39,780 --> 00:10:41,580
I don't know how they will treat you.

153
00:10:42,420 --> 00:10:43,780
Spend some money to smooth things over,

154
00:10:43,860 --> 00:10:44,900
so you can live a peaceful life.

155
00:10:44,940 --> 00:10:45,780
Miss,

156
00:10:46,180 --> 00:10:47,380
I dare not accept it.

157
00:10:47,940 --> 00:10:50,700
This is the token of love City Lord gave you.

158
00:10:58,140 --> 00:10:59,580
(Yin Ji, an adopted son from Xiao family)

159
00:11:02,420 --> 00:11:03,260
Although at that time

160
00:11:03,340 --> 00:11:05,500
he has not yet officially become City Lord,

161
00:11:05,860 --> 00:11:07,020
you treated him...

162
00:11:07,020 --> 00:11:08,700
Don't bring up the past.

163
00:11:09,700 --> 00:11:10,700
People's hearts have changed.

164
00:11:12,060 --> 00:11:12,900
Stop refusing me.

165
00:11:12,900 --> 00:11:13,740
Miss...

166
00:11:14,540 --> 00:11:15,380
Thank you, Miss.

167
00:11:22,660 --> 00:11:23,500
Xie Yun,

168
00:11:24,140 --> 00:11:25,580
Madam wanted to meet you.

169
00:11:29,100 --> 00:11:34,340
(Hanmo Pavilion)

170
00:11:37,620 --> 00:11:38,740
Greetings, My Lady.

171
00:11:39,460 --> 00:11:40,300
How dare you!

172
00:11:40,300 --> 00:11:42,380
You dare not kneel when you meet Madam.

173
00:11:42,780 --> 00:11:43,700
From today,

174
00:11:44,620 --> 00:11:46,060
I am no longer a maid in the mansion.

175
00:11:47,300 --> 00:11:48,620
According to the laws of Baiyu City,

176
00:11:49,460 --> 00:11:50,340
commoners only need to bow

177
00:11:50,940 --> 00:11:52,620
when seeing City Lord,

178
00:11:53,500 --> 00:11:54,740
let alone Madam.

179
00:11:55,220 --> 00:11:56,420
You got kicked out of City Lord's room

180
00:11:56,460 --> 00:11:58,820
before midnight every day.

181
00:11:59,220 --> 00:12:00,140
You still dare to talk tough.

182
00:12:04,020 --> 00:12:04,900
Xie Yun,

183
00:12:05,620 --> 00:12:06,620
