184
00:12:07,780 --> 00:12:09,380
You're still so aloof.

185
00:12:10,020 --> 00:12:11,380
What do you think you are?

186
00:12:11,500 --> 00:12:13,300
You dare to use Ji to suppress me.

187
00:12:13,660 --> 00:12:15,020
You are so brave!

188
00:12:22,060 --> 00:12:24,100
I have nothing to do with City Lord.

189
00:12:25,260 --> 00:12:27,540
If you want to vent your anger on someone,

190
00:12:27,740 --> 00:12:28,940
you may have picked the wrong person.

191
00:12:29,380 --> 00:12:31,020
Your words sound nice.

192
00:12:31,940 --> 00:12:34,020
Since you are aware of your identity,

193
00:12:34,380 --> 00:12:35,420
you should

194
00:12:35,500 --> 00:12:37,660
tuck in your fox tail and behave yourself.

195
00:12:37,860 --> 00:12:38,700
What?

196
00:12:39,140 --> 00:12:40,500
You get used to sleeping with different men.

197
00:12:40,980 --> 00:12:42,380
You see no hope in Yin Qi,

198
00:12:42,380 --> 00:12:43,900
