204
00:12:55,220 --> 00:12:57,780
I don't allow you to speak ill of my family.

205
00:12:58,060 --> 00:13:00,500
You dare to act but not to bear, huh?

206
00:13:00,620 --> 00:13:02,660
You are so shameless and despicable.

207
00:13:11,300 --> 00:13:12,140
