222
00:13:49,020 --> 00:13:50,340
It has nothing to do with Xiuxiu.

223
00:13:53,340 --> 00:13:54,180
Good.

224
00:14:02,900 --> 00:14:03,900
It's just a bracelet.

225
00:14:05,060 --> 00:14:06,140
It doesn't matter.

226
00:14:08,180 --> 00:14:10,740
